OL,6,FPolice are investigating the death of
OL,7,Fa soldier on an Army training exercise
OL,8,Fnear Brecon.
OL,10,FCorporal Christopher Gill of the 4th
OL,11,FBattalion, the Ranger Regiment, died
OL,12,Fduring a "non-operational incident"
OL,13,Fnear Brecon on October 16, the
OL,14,FMinistry of Defence said.
OL,16,FThe Army special operations soldier
OL,17,Fhelped train fighters in Afghanistan
OL,18,Fas well as Ukrainian soldiers in the
OL,19,FUK during his 13 years of service.
